Detailed Description

Parameters used to configure the DCAN module.

Field Documentation

uint32_t CAN_DCANCfgParams_t::autoBusOnEnable

Auto Bus on enable/disable. Valid values: 1 or 0.

uint32_t CAN_DCANCfgParams_t::autoBusOnTimerVal

Auto Bus-On Timer Value in OCP clocks Valid only when autoBusOnEnable is set.

uint32_t CAN_DCANCfgParams_t::autoRetransmitDisable

Disable Automatic retransmission of failure messages Valid values: 1 or 0.

uint32_t CAN_DCANCfgParams_t::eccDiagModeEnable

Enable/disable SECDED Diagnostic Mode Valid values: 1 or 0.

uint32_t CAN_DCANCfgParams_t::eccModeEnable

Enable/disable SECDED single bit error correction Valid values: 1 or 0.

uint32_t CAN_DCANCfgParams_t::errIntrEnable

Error Interrupt enable/disable. Valid values: 1 or 0. NOTE: Application must register a callback function, CAN_ErrStatusAppCallBack, if it needs to be notified

uint32_t CAN_DCANCfgParams_t::if1DmaEnable

IF1 DMA enable/disable. Valid values: 1 or 0.

uint32_t CAN_DCANCfgParams_t::if2DmaEnable

IF2 DMA enable/disable. Valid values: 1 or 0.

uint32_t CAN_DCANCfgParams_t::if3DmaEnable

IF3 DMA enable/disable. Valid values: 1 or 0.

uint32_t CAN_DCANCfgParams_t::intrLine0Enable

Interrupt line 0 enable/disable. Valid values: 1 or 0. Note: Must be enabled to receive error and status interrupts.

uint32_t CAN_DCANCfgParams_t::intrLine1Enable

Interrupt line 1 enable/disable. Valid values: 1 or 0. Note: Must be enabled to receive transmit complete and data receive interrupts.

uint32_t CAN_DCANCfgParams_t::parityEnable

Parity/ECC Enable or Disable Valid values: 1 or 0.

uint32_t CAN_DCANCfgParams_t::ramAccessEnable

Direct access to the RAM is enabled/disabled while in test mode Valid only when testModeEnable is set - Valid values: 1 or 0.

uint32_t CAN_DCANCfgParams_t::sbeEventEnable

Enable/disable SECDED single bit error event Valid values: 1 or 0.

uint32_t CAN_DCANCfgParams_t::stsChangeIntrEnable

Status Change Interrupt enable/disable. Valid values: 1 or 0. NOTE: Application must register a callback function, CAN_ErrStatusAppCallBack, if it needs to be notified

uint32_t CAN_DCANCfgParams_t::testMode

Test mode. For valid values refer enum CAN_DCANTestMode Valid only when testModeEnable is set,

uint32_t CAN_DCANCfgParams_t::testModeEnable

Test Mode enable/disable. Valid values: 1 or 0,
